1634  [return: NotNull]
1635  internal static int Utf8Size([NotNull] string str) => str.Validate().Length * 4 + 1;
1636 
1644  [return: NotNull]
1645  internal static byte[] Utf8Encode([NotNull] string str, [NotNull] byte[] buffer, [NotNull] int bufferSize)
1646  {
1647  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str.Validate(), 0, str.Validate().Length, buffer, 0);
1648  buffer[str.Length] = 0;
1649  return buffer;
1650  }
1651 
1657  internal static byte[] Utf8EncodeHeap(string str)
1658  {
1659  if (str == null)
1660  {
1661  return null;
1662  }
1663 
1664  int bufferSize = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(str) + 1;
1665  byte[] buffer = new byte[bufferSize];
1666  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str, 0, str.Length, buffer, 0);
1667  buffer[bufferSize - 1] = 0; // Null-terminate the string
1668 
1669  return buffer;
1670  }
1671 
1672 
1679  public static string Utf8ToManaged(IntPtr s, bool freePtr = false)
1680  {
1681  if (s == IntPtr.Zero)
1682  {
1683  return null;
1684  }
1685 
1686  int len = 0;
1687  while (Marshal.ReadByte(s, len) != 0)
1688  {
1689  len++;
1690  }
1691 
1692  if (len == 0)
1693  {
1694  return string.Empty;
1695  }
1696 
1697  byte[] bytes = new byte[len];
1698  Marshal.Copy(s, bytes, 0, len);
1699  string result = Encoding.UTF8.GetString(bytes);
1700 
1701  if (freePtr)
1702  {
1703  SDL_free(s);
1704  }
1705 
1706  return result;
1707  }

1718  private static uint SDL_FOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => (uint) (a | (b << 8) | (c << 16) | (d << 24));

2670  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
2671  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref InternalSdlMessageBoxData messageBoxData, out int buttonId);
2672 
2673 
2679  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(string str)
2680  {
2681  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
2682  {
2683  return IntPtr.Zero;
2684  }
2685 
2686  byte[] bytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0');
2687  IntPtr mem = SDL_malloc(bytes.Length);
2688  Marshal.Copy(bytes, 0, mem, bytes.Length);
2689  return mem;
2690  }
2691 
2698  public static int SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref SdlMessageBoxData messageBoxData, out int buttonId)
2699  {
2700  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
2701  {
2702  flags = messageBoxData.flags,
2703  window = messageBoxData.window,
2704  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.title),
2705  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.message),
2706  numbuttons = messageBoxData.numbuttons
2707  };
2708 
2709  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageBoxData.numbuttons];
2710  IntPtr buttonsPtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2711 
2712  try
2713  {
2714  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2715  {
2716  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
2717  {
2718  flags = messageBoxData.buttons[i].flags,
2719  buttonId = messageBoxData.buttons[i].buttonId,
2720  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.buttons[i].text)
2721  };
2722  }
2723 
2724  buttonsPtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(buttons.Length * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
2725  for (int i = 0; i < buttons.Length; i++)
2726  {
2727  IntPtr buttonPtr = buttonsPtr + i * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>();
2728  Marshal.StructureToPtr(buttons[i], buttonPtr, false);
2729  }
2730 
2731  data.buttons = buttonsPtr;
2732 
2733  IntPtr colorSchemePtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2734  if (messageBoxData.colorScheme != null)
2735  {
2736  colorSchemePtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>());
2737  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageBoxData.colorScheme.Value, colorSchemePtr, false);
2738  }
2739 
2740  int result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonId);
2741 
2742  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2743  {
2744  SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
2745  }
2746 
2747  SDL_free(data.message);
2748  SDL_free(data.title);
2749 
2750  if (colorSchemePtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2751  {
2752  Marshal.DestroyStructure<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>(colorSchemePtr);
2753  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(colorSchemePtr);
2754  }
2755 
2756  return result;
2757  }
2758  finally
2759  {
2760  if (buttonsPtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2761  {
2762  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(buttonsPtr);
2763  }
2764  }
2765  }
2766

5944  [return: NotNull]
5945  private static uint SdlDefinePixelFourcc(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => SDL_FOURCC(a, b, c, d);
5946 
5956  [return: NotNull]
5957  private static uint SdlDefinePixelFormat(
5958  SdlPixelType type,
5959  uint order,
5960  SdlPackedLayout layout,
5961  byte bits,
5962  byte bytes
5963  )
5964  => (uint) (
5965  (1 << 28) |
5966  ((byte) type << 24) |
5967  ((byte) order << 20) |
5968  ((byte) layout << 16) |
5969  (bits << 8) |
5970  bytes
5971  );
5972 
5978  [return: NotNull]
5979  private static byte SdlPixelFlag(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 28) & 0x0F);
5980 
5986  [return: NotNull]
5987  private static byte SdlPixelType(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 24) & 0x0F);
5988 
5994  [return: NotNull]
5995  private static byte SdlPixelOrder(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 20) & 0x0F);
5996 
6002  [return: NotNull]
6003  public static byte SdlPixelLayout(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 16) & 0x0F);
6004 
6010  [return: NotNull]
6011  public static byte SdlBitsPerPixel(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 8) & 0xFF);
6012 
6018  [return: NotNull]
6019  public static byte SdlBytesPerPixel(uint x)
6020  {
6021  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(x))
6022  {
6023  if (x == SdlPixelFormatYuy2 ||
6024  x == SdlPixelFormatUy ||
6025  x == SdlPixelFormatYv)
6026  {
6027  return 2;
6028  }
6029 
6030  return 1;
6031  }
6032 
6033  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
6034  }
6035 
6041  [return: NotNull]
6042  public static bool SdlIsPixelFormatIndexed(uint format)
6043  {
6044  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
6045  {
6046  return false;
6047  }
6048 
6049  SdlPixelType pType =
6050  (SdlPixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
6051  return pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex1 ||
6052  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex4 ||
6053  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex8;
6054  }
6055 
6061  [return: NotNull]
6062  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatPacked(uint format)
6063  {
6064  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
6065  {
6066  return false;
6067  }
6068 
6069  SdlPixelType pType =
6070  (SdlPixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
6071  return pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked8 ||
6072  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked16 ||
6073  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked32;
6074  }
6075 
6081  [return: NotNull]
6082  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatArray(uint format)
6083  {
6084  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
6085  {
6086  return false;
6087  }
6088 
6089  SdlPixelType pType =
6090  (SdlPixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
6091  return pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu8 ||
6092  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu16 ||
6093  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu32 ||
6094  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf16 ||
6095  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf32;
6096  }
6097 
6103  [return: NotNull]
6104  public static bool SdlIsPixelFormatAlpha(uint format)
6105  {
6106  if (SdlIsPixelFormatPacked(format))
6107  {
6108  SdlPackedOrder pOrder =
6109  (SdlPackedOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
6110  return pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderArgb ||
6111  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderRgba ||
6112  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderAbgr ||
6113  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderBgra;
6114  }
6115 
6116  if (SdlIsPixelFormatArray(format))
6117  {
6118  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
6119  (SdlArrayOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
6120  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
6121  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
6122  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
6123  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
6124  }
6125 
6126  return false;
6127  }
6128 
6134  [return: NotNull]
6135  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatFour(uint format) => (format == 0) && (SdlPixelFlag(format) != 1);

7105  out SdlEventFilter filter,
7106  out IntPtr userdata
7107  )

7110  if (result != IntPtr.Zero)

7113  result,
7114  typeof(SdlEventFilter)

7117  else

7120  }
7121 
7122  return val;
